nga<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a name=\\\"_GoBack\\\"><\\/a><em>Tel:<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<\\/em><em>+<\\/em><em>255-272977124<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Fax:<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<em>+255-<em>272977125<\\/em><\\/em><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Email::<\\/em><em>&nbsp;tanga@tpsc.go.tz<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"particulars_en\":\"<p>Who are we?<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Tanzania Public Service College (TPSC) Tanga campus was established in July 2014, being the fourth campus to be established among the six campuses of TPSC. It&rsquo;s establishment was a result of instructions issued by prime minister Hon. Mizengo Pinda on 23th November 2009 during inauguration of Tanzania Public Service College Mtwara Campus.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>At the time of its establishment, it had only one academic programme (i.e. Basic Technician Certificate in Records Management), with 453 students and 9 instructors. At the moment the college has over 5 courses, with more than 50 instructors and over 1,600 students.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_en\":\"<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>Records, Archives and Information Management<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Secretarial Studies<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Human Resource Management<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Public Administration<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Procurement and Supply Management<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"student_services_en\":\"<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Career counselling&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Healthcare<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Networking training and events<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Student counsellor<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Student sports<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Students Organizations<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"facilities_en\":\"<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Study training and workshops<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Typing and Computer labs<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Hostel<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Canteen<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><span style=\\\"font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#1d1d1b\\\">Stationaries<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"contacts_en\":\"<p><em>Campus Director ,<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Tanzania Public Service College<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>P.O. Box 750<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Tanga<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a name=\\\"_GoBack\\\"><\\/a><em>Tel:<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<\\/em><em>+<\\/em><em>255-272977124<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Fax:<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<em>+255-<em>272977125<\\/em><\\/em><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Email::<\\/em><em>&nbsp;tanga@tpsc.go.tz<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"tanga\",\"title_sw\":\"Kampasi ya Tanga\",\"title_en\":\"Tanga Campus\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-15T09:51:45.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-15T09:51:45.000000Z\"}','2023-12-15 06:53:55','2023-12-15 06:53:55'),(1251,6,'Campus','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/campuses','{\"title_sw\":\"Kampasi ya Mtwara\",\"title_en\":\"Mtwara Campus\",\"particulars_sw\":\"<p>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Kampasi ya Mtwara kilizinduliwa na Waziri Mkuu Mh. Mizengo Peter Pinda Tarehe 23 Novemba, 2009.Katika uzinduzi huo kampasi ilikuwa na jumla ya wanafunzi 261 na watumishi 7.Kwa sasa Kampasi ina wanafunzi zaidi ya 2000 na watumishi 57.Mwanzoni Kampasi hii ilikusudiwa kuhudumia Kanda na Mikoa mitatu (Mtwara, Lindi na Ruvuma) kwa sababu za mazingira yao ya kijografia na historia kimeshindwa kuvutia watu kusafiri kuja Dar es salaam na Tabora kwa ajili ya mafunzo zaidi. Kwa hiyo Kampasi ya Mtwara pamekuwa mahali pa kuanzia kwa watu wa Mikoa ya Kusini kujiunga na mafunzo ya elimu ya juu.Kwa sasa Kampasi ya Mtwara inatoa mafunzo kwa Mikoa ya Kusini pamoja na Mikoa yote ya Tanzania.Ina wanafunzi takribani kutoka kila Mkoa wa Tanzania.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Tuko wapi?<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Kampasi ya Mtwara (TPSC) ipo sehemu yakusini ya Tanzania katika Mkoa wa Mtwara, eneo la Shangani Mashariki, karibu na Nyumba za Shirika la Nyumba Tanzania Shangani na Hospitali ya Tawi la Ndanda.Kama ukiwa Kituo Kikuu chaMabasi cha Mkoa au mahali kwengine kokote katika Mji wa Mtwara, Chukua Usafiri wa Bodaboda mwambie derive akupeleke &ldquo;Chuo cha Utumishi Mtwara&rdquo;<\\/p>\",\"particulars_en\":\"<p>TPSC Mtwara campus is a branch of Tanzania Public Service College which was officially inaugurated by the Prime Minister Honourable Mizengo Peter Pinda on the 23rd November 2009. At its inauguration, it had a total of 261 students with 7 staffs. Currently, it has over 2,000 students with 57 staffs. Initially the campus was aimed at catering the three southern zonal regions (Mtwara, Lindi and Ruvuma) as their geographical and historical background failed to attract people travelling to Dar es Salaam and Tabora to pursue their further studies. Hence Mtwara Campus has been a stepping stone for southern regions people to join to higher studies.<br \\/>\\r\\nIn the mean time, TPSC Mtwara is not only serving the southern regions but all regions in Tanzania. It has students comming from almost every regions in Tanzania.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Where are We?<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>TPSC Mtwara campus is locate at the Southern part ofTanzania, in Mtwara region, at the Shangani East area, near National housing houses Shangani and Ndanda branch hospital. If you are at the main regional bus stand (or any where around Mtwara town), pick a Bodaboda and ask the driver to bring you to &quot;Chuo cha utumishi Mtwara&quot;<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_sw\":\"<p>Utunzaji wa kumbukumbu.......\\/.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_en\":\"<p>Records and archaive management........<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"student_services_sw\":\"<p>Hostel<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Huduma za Afya<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Dawati la jinsia<\\/p>\",\"student_services_en\":\"<p>Accomodation<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Health services through NHIF<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Students service help desk<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Studentd ID<\\/p>\",\"facilities_sw\":\"<p>Kampasi ya Mtwara ina miundombinu ifuatayo:,&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Maabara za kompyuta,<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Maabara ya kupiga chapa<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Madarasa<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Hosteli<\\/p>\",\"facilities_en\":\"<p>Full furnished Class rooms,<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Computer laboratories,<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Typing labs<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Libray facilities<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Cafeteria services<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>,&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contacts_sw\":\"<p><em>Mkurugenzi wa Kampasi<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>S.L.P 1051<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Mtwara<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Simu:<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<\\/em>: +255 232 333300<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Nukushi<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<\\/em>+255 232 333300<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Barua Pepe:<\\/em><em>&nbsp;<\\/em>mtwara@tpsc.go.tz<\\/p>\",\"contacts_en\":\"<p>Campus Director<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>TPSC Mtwara Campus<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>P.O.Box 1051<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mtwara<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Phone: +255 232 333300<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Fax: +255 232 333300<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Email: mtwara@tpsc.go.tz<\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"mtwara-campus\"}','2023-12-15 06:56:56','2023-12-15 06:56:56'),(1252,6,'Campus','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/campuses','{\"title_sw\":\"Sehemu ya Mafunzo kwa Njia ya Mtandao\",\"title_en\":\"Global Learning Section\",\"particulars_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">The Global Learning Centre (GLC) is a Directorate of Tanzania Public Service College (TPSC). It is a capacity building centre with wide-range capacity building interventions that include; Leadership and Managerial Skills development, Board Governance and Leadership, Fraud investigation, Fundamentals of Regulation in Utility Services and other regulatory areas (water, oil, electricity and Gas, weather), Change Management, Transformation Leadership, Financial management, Project management, Team Building and Coaching, Human Resource management, Counselling and Guidance, and Enterprise Risk Management. GLC is also a member of the Global Development<br \\/>\\r\\nLearning Network (GDLN) which is a partnership of over 120 recognised global institutions (ffiliates) in over 80 countries that collaborates in the design of customised learning solutions for individuals and organisations working in development.<\\/p>\",\"particulars_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">The Global Learning Centre (GLC) is a Directorate of Tanzania Public Service College (TPSC). It is a capacity building centre with wide-range capacity building interventions that include; Leadership and Managerial Skills development, Board Governance and Leadership, Fraud investigation, Fundamentals of Regulation in Utility Services and other regulatory areas (water, oil, electricity and Gas, weather), Change Management, Transformation Leadership, Financial management, Project management, Team Building and Coaching, Human Resource management, Counselling and Guidance, and Enterprise Risk Management. GLC is also a member of the Global Development<br \\/>\\r\\nLearning Network (GDLN) which is a partnership of over 120 recognised global institutions (ffiliates) in over 80 countries that collaborates in the design of customised learning solutions for individuals and organisations working in development.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_sw\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_en\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"student_services_sw\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"student_services_en\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"facilities_sw\":\"<p>-.<\\/p>\",\"facilities_en\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"contacts_sw\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"contacts_en\":\"<p>.<\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"global-learning-section\"}','2023-12-15 07:00:46','2023-12-15 07:00:46'),(1253,6,'Campus','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/campuses/7','{\"id\":7,\"particulars_sw\":\"<p><strong>Kampasi ya Tabora kwa Ufupi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania (TPSC) Kampasi ya Tabora kilichokuwa kikijulikana kwa jina la Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora ni Kampasi ya pili ya zamani baada ya Kampasi ya Dar es Salaam kilichokuwa kikijulikana kama Chuo cha Mafunzo ya Utumishi wa Serikali. Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora kilianzishwa ili kujaza pengo la upungufu wa watumishi wa Ofisini na hasa Wahazili baada ya kupata Uhuru Tanzania. Ujenzi wa Chuo ulianza Septemba 1970 na kukamilika na kuanza kufanya kazi Oktoba, 1973. Chuo hiki kimekuwa na mabweni manne ya wanafunzi 600, wanaume 300 na wanawake 300 na maeneo ya michezo na burudani.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mwaka 2000 Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora na Chuo cha Mafunzo cha Utumishi wa Serikali viliunda Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kwa Sheria ya Wakala za Serikali Na. ya 2000.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Wakati wa kuanzishwa kwake ilikuwa na mihula miwili ya wiki 21 kwa mwaka, hasa kutilia mkazo Mafunzo ya awali na Mafunzo tarajali ya Uhazili na wakufunzi 29 tu. Hivi sasa Kampasi hii ina zaidi ya kozi 5, na wakufunzi wa kudumu 23 na wa muda 21 na Zaidi ya wanafunzi 2563 wanachukua program za Cheti na Diploma.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em><u>Tuko wapi?<\\/u><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania Kampasi ya Tabora kipo Mtaa wa Itetemya, Kata ya Kanyenye Manispaa ya Tabora mkabala na Makao makuu ya&nbsp; Polisi mkoa wa Tabora.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_sw\":\"<p>The following programmes are offered at Tabora Campus;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>Uhazili (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Utunzaji Kumbukumbu, Nyaraka, na Taarifa (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Menejimenti ya Rasilimali watu (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"student_services_sw\":\"<p><strong>Huduma za Malazi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Huduma za Afya<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Dawati la Jinsia<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Ushauri Nasaha<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Serikali ya Wanafunzi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\",\"facilities_sw\":\"<p><strong>Madarasa<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maabara za Upigaji Chapa<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maabara za Kompyuta<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maktaba<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contacts_sw\":\"<p><em>Mkurugenzi wa Kampasi<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>S.L.P 329<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><strong>Tabora<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Simu: +255 26 260 5387<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Nukusi: +255 26 260 45 37<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Barua Pepe: <a>tabora@tpsc.go.tz<\\/a><\\/em><\\/p>\",\"particulars_en\":\"<p><strong>Tabora Campus overview<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania (TPSC) Kampasi ya Tabora kilichokuwa kikijulikana kwa jina la Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora ni Kampasi ya pili ya zamani baada ya Kampasi ya Dar es Salaam kilichokuwa kikijulikana kama Chuo cha Mafunzo ya Utumishi wa Serikali. Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora kilianzishwa ili kujaza pengo la upungufu wa watumishi wa Ofisini na hasa Wahazili baada ya kupata Uhuru Tanzania. Ujenzi wa Chuo ulianza Septemba 1970 na kukamilika na kuanza kufanya kazi Oktoba, 1973. Chuo hiki kimekuwa na mabweni manne ya wanafunzi 600, wanaume 300 na wanawake 300 na maeneo ya michezo na burudani.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mwaka 2000 Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora na Chuo cha Mafunzo cha Utumishi wa Serikali viliunda Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kwa Sheria ya Wakala za Serikali Na. ya 2000.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Wakati wa kuanzishwa kwake ilikuwa na mihula miwili ya wiki 21 kwa mwaka, hasa kutilia mkazo Mafunzo ya awali na Mafunzo tarajali ya Uhazili na wakufunzi 29 tu. Hivi sasa Kampasi hii ina zaidi ya kozi 5, na wakufunzi wa kudumu 23 na wa muda 21 na Zaidi ya wanafunzi 2563 wanachukua program za Cheti na Diploma.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em><u>Tuko wapi?<\\/u><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania Kampasi ya Tabora kipo Mtaa wa Itetemya, Kata ya Kanyenye Manispaa ya Tabora mkabala na Makao makuu ya&nbsp; Polisi mkoa wa Tabora.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_en\":\"<p>The following programmes are offered at Tabora Campus;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>Secretarial Studies (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Records, Archives and Information Management (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Human Resource Management (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"student_services_en\":\"<p><strong>Accomodation<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Health Service<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Gender Issues<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Guidance and Support<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Students&#39; Government<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Cafeteria Services<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\",\"facilities_en\":\"<p><strong>Madarasa<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maabara za Upigaji Chapa<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maabara za Kompyuta<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maktaba<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\",\"contacts_en\":\"<p><em>Campus Director<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Tanzania Public Service College<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>P.O BOX 329,<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><strong>Tabora<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Phone: +255 26 260 5387<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Fax: +255 26 260 45 37<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Email: <a>tabora@tpsc.go.tz<\\/a><\\/em><\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"kampasi-ya-tabora\",\"title_sw\":\"TABORA CAMPUS\",\"title_en\":\"KAMPASI YA TABORA\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-15T09:52:42.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-15T09:52:42.000000Z\"}','2023-12-15 07:03:11','2023-12-15 07:03:11'),(1254,6,'Campus','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/campuses/7','{\"id\":7,\"particulars_sw\":\"<p><strong>Kampasi ya Tabora kwa Ufupi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania (TPSC) Kampasi ya Tabora kilichokuwa kikijulikana kwa jina la Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora ni Kampasi ya pili ya zamani baada ya Kampasi ya Dar es Salaam kilichokuwa kikijulikana kama Chuo cha Mafunzo ya Utumishi wa Serikali. Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora kilianzishwa ili kujaza pengo la upungufu wa watumishi wa Ofisini na hasa Wahazili baada ya kupata Uhuru Tanzania. Ujenzi wa Chuo ulianza Septemba 1970 na kukamilika na kuanza kufanya kazi Oktoba, 1973. Chuo hiki kimekuwa na mabweni manne ya wanafunzi 600, wanaume 300 na wanawake 300 na maeneo ya michezo na burudani.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mwaka 2000 Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora na Chuo cha Mafunzo cha Utumishi wa Serikali viliunda Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kwa Sheria ya Wakala za Serikali Na. ya 2000.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Wakati wa kuanzishwa kwake ilikuwa na mihula miwili ya wiki 21 kwa mwaka, hasa kutilia mkazo Mafunzo ya awali na Mafunzo tarajali ya Uhazili na wakufunzi 29 tu. Hivi sasa Kampasi hii ina zaidi ya kozi 5, na wakufunzi wa kudumu 23 na wa muda 21 na Zaidi ya wanafunzi 2563 wanachukua program za Cheti na Diploma.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em><u>Tuko wapi?<\\/u><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania Kampasi ya Tabora kipo Mtaa wa Itetemya, Kata ya Kanyenye Manispaa ya Tabora mkabala na Makao makuu ya&nbsp; Polisi mkoa wa Tabora.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_sw\":\"<p>The following programmes are offered at Tabora Campus;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>Uhazili (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Utunzaji Kumbukumbu, Nyaraka, na Taarifa (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Menejimenti ya Rasilimali watu (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"student_services_sw\":\"<p><strong>Huduma za Malazi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Huduma za Afya<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Dawati la Jinsia<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Ushauri Nasaha<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Serikali ya Wanafunzi<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\",\"facilities_sw\":\"<p><strong>Madarasa<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maabara za Upigaji Chapa<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maabara za Kompyuta<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Maktaba<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contacts_sw\":\"<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Mkurugenzi wa Kampasi<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>S.L.P 329<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><strong>Tabora<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Simu: +255 26 260 5387<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Nukusi: +255 26 260 45 37<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Barua Pepe: <a>tabora@tpsc.go.tz<\\/a><\\/em><\\/p>\",\"particulars_en\":\"<p><strong>Tabora Campus overview<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania (TPSC) Kampasi ya Tabora kilichokuwa kikijulikana kwa jina la Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora ni Kampasi ya pili ya zamani baada ya Kampasi ya Dar es Salaam kilichokuwa kikijulikana kama Chuo cha Mafunzo ya Utumishi wa Serikali. Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora kilianzishwa ili kujaza pengo la upungufu wa watumishi wa Ofisini na hasa Wahazili baada ya kupata Uhuru Tanzania. Ujenzi wa Chuo ulianza Septemba 1970 na kukamilika na kuanza kufanya kazi Oktoba, 1973. Chuo hiki kimekuwa na mabweni manne ya wanafunzi 600, wanaume 300 na wanawake 300 na maeneo ya michezo na burudani.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mwaka 2000 Chuo cha Uhazili Tabora na Chuo cha Mafunzo cha Utumishi wa Serikali viliunda Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kwa Sheria ya Wakala za Serikali Na. ya 2000.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Wakati wa kuanzishwa kwake ilikuwa na mihula miwili ya wiki 21 kwa mwaka, hasa kutilia mkazo Mafunzo ya awali na Mafunzo tarajali ya Uhazili na wakufunzi 29 tu. Hivi sasa Kampasi hii ina zaidi ya kozi 5, na wakufunzi wa kudumu 23 na wa muda 21 na Zaidi ya wanafunzi 2563 wanachukua program za Cheti na Diploma.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em><u>Tuko wapi?<\\/u><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania Kampasi ya Tabora kipo Mtaa wa Itetemya, Kata ya Kanyenye Manispaa ya Tabora mkabala na Makao makuu ya&nbsp; Polisi mkoa wa Tabora.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_en\":\"<p>The following programmes are offered at Tabora Campus;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>Secretarial Studies (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Records, Archives and Information Management (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Human Resource Management (NTAL Level 4 to NTA Level 6)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"student_services_en\":\"<p><strong>Accomodation<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Health Service<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Gender Issues<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Guidance and Support<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Students&#39; Government<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Cafeteria Services<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-----<\\/p>\",\"facilities_en\":\"<p><strong>Madara