trong>Slide Design and Layout:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Themes, layouts, and formatting options<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Adding multimedia elements<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Presentation Delivery:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Rehearsing and delivering presentations<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Incorporating speaker notes and transitions<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Module 5: Internet and Communication<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Internet Basics:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Web browsers, search engines, and URLs<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Safe internet browsing practices<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Email Communication:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Sending and receiving emails<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Email etiquette and best practices<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Module 6: Basic Computer Security<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Password Management:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Creating strong passwords<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Password best practices<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Antivirus and Malware Protection:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Understanding and using antivirus software<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Recognizing and avoiding malware<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Module 7: File Management and Backup<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Organizing Files and Folders:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Creating a file hierarchy<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Renaming and moving files<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Data Backup:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Importance of data backup<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Creating backups and restoring data<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Module 8: Practical Applications and Projects<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Hands-On Projects:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Applying learned skills in real-world scenarios<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Creating documents, spreadsheets, and presentations<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Troubleshooting Basics:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Basic problem-solving strategies<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Common issues and solutions<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Module 9: Emerging Technologies<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li><strong>Introduction to Emerging Technologies:<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Overview of current and future trends (e.g., AI, IoT)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Exploring new technologies<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Module 10: Review and Assessment<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Course Review:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Recap of key concepts and skills<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Q&amp;A and clarification of doubts<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Assessment:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Evaluation through quizzes, assignments, or a final project<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Certification for successful completion<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>This course structure provides participants with a well-rounded understanding of basic computer applications and prepares them for practical use in both personal and professional contexts. The hands-on projects and practical applications ensure that participants gain valuable experience applying the skills they&#39;ve learned.<\\/p>\",\"expected_benefit_sw\":\"<p>A Basic Computer Application course offers numerous benefits for individuals who participate, regardless of their background or current skill level. Here are some key advantages:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Enhanced Employability:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Acquiring basic computer skills enhances employability in various industries. Many job roles require at least a fundamental understanding of common software applications and computer usage.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Access to Educational Resources:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Basic computer skills enable individuals to access educational resources online, enhancing their ability to learn and stay informed on various subjects.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Improved Communication:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Learning email basics and using communication tools allows individuals to stay connected with others, fostering improved communication in both personal and professional settings.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Efficient Information Management:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Understanding file management and basic software applications helps individuals organize and manage information efficiently, whether for personal use or work-related tasks.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Increased Productivity:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Proficiency in applications such as word processors and spreadsheets contributes to increased productivity, allowing individuals to create documents, analyze data, and perform routine tasks more efficiently.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"expected_benefit_en\":\"<p>A Basic Computer Application course offers numerous benefits for individuals who participate, regardless of their background or current skill level. Here are some key advantages:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Enhanced Employability:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Acquiring basic computer skills enhances employability in various industries. Many job roles require at least a fundamental understanding of common software applications and computer usage.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Access to Educational Resources:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Basic computer skills enable individuals to access educational resources online, enhancing their ability to learn and stay informed on various subjects.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Improved Communication:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Learning email basics and using communication tools allows individuals to stay connected with others, fostering improved communication in both personal and professional settings.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Efficient Information Management:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Understanding file management and basic software applications helps individuals organize and manage information efficiently, whether for personal use or work-related tasks.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<p><strong>Increased Productivity:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t<ul>\\r\\n\\t\\t<li>Proficiency in applications such as word processors and spreadsheets contributes to increased productivity, allowing individuals to create documents, analyze data, and perform routine tasks more efficiently.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"course_coodinator_sw\":\"<p>John Johnson<\\/p>\",\"course_coodinator_en\":\"<p>John Johnson<\\/p>\",\"course_detail_id\":13,\"course_type\":2}','2023-12-15 07:16:21','2023-12-15 07:16:21'),(1262,6,'ShortCourse','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/short_courses','{\"title_sw\":\"EFFECTIVE CORPORATE GOVERNANCE\",\"title_en\":\"EFFECTIVE CORPORATE GOVERNANCE\",\"category_en\":\"Management and Leadership\",\"category_sw\":\"Management and Leadership\",\"start_date\":\"2023-12-18\",\"end_date\":\"2023-12-22\",\"venue_en\":\"AICC - Arusha\",\"venue_sw\":\"AICC - Arusha\",\"slug\":\"effective-corporate-governance\"}','2023-12-15 07:21:55','2023-12-15 07:21:55'),(1263,6,'CourseDetail','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/short_courses','{\"description_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">The role and scope of the governing body are diverse however among others is to sets top tone of the organization by instituting the good governance and performance standards, ethical culture, effective control and legitimacy with stakeholders to achieve organization goals. &nbsp;Corporate governance plays a crucial role in ensuring the effective management, accountability, and sustainability of organizations.&nbsp; By participating in this Board Induction training, participants&nbsp;&nbsp;will gain the knowledge and skills necessary to make informed decisions, provide effective oversight, and contribute to the strategic direction of the organisation.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"description_en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">The role and scope of the governing body are diverse however among others is to sets top tone of the organization by instituting the good governance and performance standards, ethical culture, effective control and legitimacy with stakeholders to achieve organization goals. &nbsp;Corporate governance plays a crucial role in ensuring the effective management, accountability, and sustainability of organizations.&nbsp; By participating in this Board Induction training, participants&nbsp;&nbsp;will gain the knowledge and skills necessary to make informed decisions, provide effective oversight, and contribute to the strategic direction of the organisation.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"target_audience_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">Board&nbsp; Members and Management&nbsp; Team .<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"target_audience_en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">Board&nbsp; Members and Management&nbsp; Team.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"course_overview_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">The Board Induction training on Corporate Governance is a comprehensive programme designed specifically for the newly appointed Board. This training aims to equip the Commissioners with the necessary knowledge, skills, and insights to effectively fulfil their roles and responsibilities as board members. Through interactive sessions, case studies, group discussions, and practical exercises, the Commissioners will gain a deep understanding of corporate governance principles, regulatory frameworks, risk management, stakeholder engagement, ethical leadership, and compliance. The training will be conducted by experienced trainer (s) who have a proven track record of delivering high-quality training programmes to similar institutions. The Commissioners will be equipped with the necessary tools to contribute effectively to board discussions, make informed decisions, ensure transparency and accountability, and advance the mission&nbsp; in promoting and regulating science and technology&nbsp;in&nbsp;Tanzania<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"course_overview_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">The Board Induction training on Corporate Governance is a comprehensive programme designed specifically for the newly appointed Board. This training aims to equip the Commissioners with the necessary knowledge, skills, and insights to effectively fulfil their roles and responsibilities as board members. Through interactive sessions, case studies, group discussions, and practical exercises, the Commissioners will gain a deep understanding of corporate governance principles, regulatory frameworks, risk management, stakeholder engagement, ethical leadership, and compliance. The training will be conducted by experienced trainer (s) who have a proven track record of delivering high-quality training programmes to similar institutions. The Commissioners will be equipped with the necessary tools to contribute effectively to board discussions, make informed decisions, ensure transparency and accountability, and advance the mission&nbsp; in promoting and regulating science and technology&nbsp;in&nbsp;Tanzania<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"expected_benefit_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">At the end of training, participants will be able;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Understanding of Corporate Governance: Develop a comprehensive understanding of corporate governance principles, frameworks, and best practices relevant to&nbsp; enabling members to effectively discharge their responsibilities as board members;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Role and Responsibilities: Gain clarity on roles and responsibilities of Commissioners, including fiduciary duties, strategic oversight, and accountability to stakeholders;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Regulatory Compliance: Understand the regulatory landscape governing science and technology in Tanzania and ensure compliance with applicable laws, regulations, and ethical standards;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Board Effectiveness: Enhance their ability to contribute effectively to board discussions, make informed decisions, and promote transparency, accountability, and ethical conduct within.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Risk Management: Develop an understanding of risk management principles and strategies, enabling to identify, assess, and mitigate risks associated with&nbsp; operations and programmes; and <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Ethical Leadership: Promote a culture of ethical leadership, integrity, and professionalism within or ensuring the highest standards of conduct and accountability.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"expected_benefit_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\">At the end of training, participants will be able;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Understanding of Corporate Governance: Develop a comprehensive understanding of corporate governance principles, frameworks, and best practices relevant to&nbsp; enabling members to effectively discharge their responsibilities as board members;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Role and Responsibilities: Gain clarity on roles and responsibilities of Commissioners, including fiduciary duties, strategic oversight, and accountability to stakeholders;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Regulatory Compliance: Understand the regulatory landscape governing science and technology in Tanzania and ensure compliance with applicable laws, regulations, and ethical standards;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Board Effectiveness: Enhance their ability to contribute effectively to board discussions, make informed decisions, and promote transparency, accountability, and ethical conduct within.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Risk Management: Develop an understanding of risk management principles and strategies, enabling to identify, assess, and mitigate risks associated with&nbsp; operations and programmes; and <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#252525\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,serif\\\">Ethical Leadership: Promote a culture of ethical leadership, integrity, and professionalism within or ensuring the highest standards of conduct and accountability.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"course_coodinator_sw\":\"<p>Frank Msewa<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Global learning section&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>0654342428<\\/p>\",\"course_coodinator_en\":\"<p>Frank Msewa<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Global learning section&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>0654342428<\\/p>\",\"course_detail_id\":14,\"course_type\":2}','2023-12-15 07:21:55','2023-12-15 07:21:55'),(1264,6,'ShortCourse','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/short_courses','{\"title_sw\":\"Usimamizi wa Rasilimali watu\",\"title_en\":\"Human Resources Management\",\"category_en\":\"Category\",\"category_sw\":\"Aina ya mafunzo\",\"start_date\":\"2024-08-02\",\"end_date\":\"2024-12-01\",\"venue_en\":\"Global Learning Center\",\"venue_sw\":\"Kituo cha Kuendesha mafunzo kwa Njia ya Mtandao\",\"slug\":\"human-resources-management\"}','2023-12-15 07:27:11','2023-12-15 07:27:11'),(1265,6,'CourseDetail','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/short_courses','{\"description_sw\":\"<p><strong>COURSE OVERVIEW<\\/strong><br \\/>\\r\\nOffice assistants typically work with others to make sure that an office functions better. They provide administrative and clerical support for proper functioning of organization offices. They must have many skills in order to perform their duties effectively. These skills are technical, administrative, interpersonal and conceptual. Technical skills are essential for understanding and executing specific duties and clerical routine tasks. Administrative abilities enable one to understand and follow policies and procedures in order to carry out organizational activities in an orderly manner. Interpersonal skills consist of the abilities to understand other people and interact effectively with them. Conceptual skills involve the ability to acquire, analyze, and interpret information in a logical manner. The above skills form the basis of important management and administrative activities such as front office management, customer care, records management, information management, office hygiene etc.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>TOPICS INCLUDE<\\/strong><br \\/>\\r\\nOffice management;<br \\/>\\r\\nAdministrative services management;<br \\/>\\r\\nManagement functions;<br \\/>\\r\\nRecords management;<br \\/>\\r\\nProblem solving and decision making;<br \\/>\\r\\nInterpersonal and communication skills;<br \\/>\\r\\nCustomer care ;<br \\/>\\r\\nPersonal effectiveness;<br \\/>\\r\\nTeam working skills;<br \\/>\\r\\nTime management;<br \\/>\\r\\nManaging stress;<br \\/>\\r\\nOffice hygiene and etiquette.<\\/p>\",\"description_en\":\"<p><strong>TOPICS INCLUDE<\\/strong><br \\/>\\r\\nOffice management;<br \\/>\\r\\nAdministrative services management;<br \\/>\\r\\nManagement functions;<br \\/>\\r\\nRecords management;<br \\/>\\r\\nProblem solving and decision making;<br \\/>\\r\\nInterpersonal and communication skills;<br \\/>\\r\\nCustomer care ;<br \\/>\\r\\nPersonal effectiveness;<br \\/>\\r\\nTeam working skills;<br \\/>\\r\\nTime management;<br \\/>\\r\\nManaging stress;<br \\/>\\r\\nOffice hygiene and etiquette.<\\/p>\",\"target_audience_sw\":\"<p><strong>WHO SHOULD ATTEND?<\\/strong><br \\/>\\r\\nAll office assistants and people newly appointed to supervisory roles, along with Secretaries and record clerks within the office environment, who want to build on their skills and knowledge<\\/p>\",\"target_audience_en\":\"<p><strong>WHO SHOULD ATTEND?<\\/strong><br \\/>\\r\\nAll office assistants and people newly appointed to supervisory roles, along with Secretaries and record clerks within the office environment, who want to build on their skills and knowledge<\\/p>\",\"course_overview_sw\":\"<p>Office assistants typically work with others to make sure that an office functions better. They provide administrative and clerical support for proper functioning of organization offices. They must have many skills in order to perform their duties effectively. These skills are technical, administrative, interpersonal and conceptual. Technical skills are essential for understanding and executing specific duties and clerical routine tasks. Administrative abilities enable one to understand and follow policies and procedures in order to carry out organizational activities in an orderly manner. Interpersonal skills consist of the abilities to understand other people and interact effectively with them. Conceptual skills involve the ability to acquire, analyze, and interpret information in a logical manner. The above skills form the basis of important management and administrative activities such as front office management, customer care, records management, information management, office hygiene etc.<\\/p>\",\"course_overview_en\":\"<p>Office assistants typically work with others to make sure that an office functions better. They provide administrative and clerical support for proper functioning of organization offices. They must have many skills in order to perform their duties effectively. These skills are technical, administrative, interpersonal and conceptual. Technical skills are essential for understanding and executing specific duties and clerical routine tasks. Administrative abilities enable one to understand and follow policies and procedures in order to carry out organizational activities in an orderly manner. Interpersonal skills consist of the abilities to understand other people and interact effectively with them. Conceptual skills involve the ability to acquire, analyze, and interpret information in a logical manner. The above skills form the basis of important management and administrative activities such as front office management, customer care, records management, information management, office hygiene etc.<\\/p>\",\"expected_benefit_sw\":\"<p><strong>HOW PARTICIPANTS WILL BENEFIT?<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>At the end of the course, participants will be able to:<br \\/>\\r\\nEnhance their personal effectiveness and development;<br \\/>\\r\\nPerform office and administrative functions effectively and efficiently;<br \\/>\\r\\nImprove ability to independently with less supervision;<br \\/>\\r\\nDeal with day to day work problems more effectively;<br \\/>\\r\\nImprove relationships with colleagues and customers;<br \\/>\\r\\nCommunicate more effectively;<br \\/>\\r\\nProvide better care to customers;<br \\/>\\r\\nEnhance hygiene in the work place;<br \\/>\\r\\nApply proper etiquettes at all times;<br \\/>\\r\\nHandle stressful situations.<\\/p>\",\"expected_benefit_en\":\"<p>At the end of the course, participants will be able to:<br \\/>\\r\\nEnhance their personal effectiveness and development;<br \\/>\\r\\nPerform office and administrative functions effectively and efficiently;<br \\/>\\r\\nImprove ability to independently with less supervision;<br \\/>\\r\\nDeal with day to day work problems more effectively;<br \\/>\\r\\nImprove relationships with colleagues and customers;<br \\/>\\r\\nCommunicate more effectively;<br \\/>\\r\\nProvide better care to customers;<br \\/>\\r\\nEnhance hygiene in the work place;<br \\/>\\r\\nApply proper etiquettes at all times;<br \\/>\\r\\nHandle stressful situations.<\\/p>\",\"course_coodinator_sw\":\"<p>Kitengo cha mafunzo ya muda mfupi<\\/p>\",\"course_coodinator_en\":\"<p>Short course department<\\/p>\",\"course_detail_id\":15,\"course_type\":2}','2023-12-15 07:27:11','2023-12-15 07:27:11'),(1266,6,'MenuItem','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/menu-items/93','{\"id\":93,\"title_sw\":\"Kozi za Muda Mfupi\",\"title_en\":\"Short Course Programmes\",\"status\":1,\"menu_id\":\"12\",\"url\":\"short_courses\",\"url_external\":null,\"link\":\"1\",\"parent\