"<p>ewguhbijj<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"name_en\":\"Shakiru\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-15T11:47:10.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-15T11:50:38.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"mr\",\"name_sw\":\"Shakiru\",\"photo_url\":\"27eeec0cce911af0f21d7ba04e8d8b1b.png\",\"user_id\":6}','2023-12-15 08:51:15','2023-12-15 08:51:15'),(1286,6,'Quotation','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/quotations','{\"title_en\":\"Bi\",\"title_sw\":\"Ms\",\"name_en\":\"Bahati\",\"name_sw\":\"Bahati\",\"content_en\":\"<p>The member of parliamment (MP) hanourable Ms Bahati worked in TPSC as an Accountant from 2015-2020<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>The member of parliamment (MP) hanourable Ms Bahati worked in TPSC as an Accountant from 2015-2020<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"9b7e5810c099c89e49486a689948e909.jpeg\",\"user_id\":6,\"slug\":\"bi\"}','2023-12-15 08:54:33','2023-12-15 08:54:33'),(1287,6,'Quotation','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/quotations/5','{\"id\":5,\"title_en\":\"Bi. Bahati Kenneth\",\"title_sw\":\"Ms. Bahati Kenneth\",\"content_en\":\"<p>The member of parliamment (MP) hanourable Ms Bahati worked in TPSC as an Accountant from 2015-2020<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>The member of parliamment (MP) hanourable Ms Bahati worked in TPSC as an Accountant from 2015-2020<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"name_en\":\"Bahati\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-15T11:54:33.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-15T11:54:33.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"bi\",\"name_sw\":\"Bahati\",\"photo_url\":\"9b7e5810c099c89e49486a689948e909.jpeg\",\"user_id\":6}','2023-12-15 08:56:43','2023-12-15 08:56:43'),(1288,6,'Quotation','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/quotations','{\"title_en\":\"Jerome Mwakyembe\",\"title_sw\":\"Jerome Mwakyembe\",\"name_en\":\".\",\"name_sw\":\".\",\"content_en\":\"<p>&ldquo;The Tanzania Public Service College&quot; was an incredibly valuable endeavor which made me develop my skills and professional insights<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>&ldquo;The Tanzania Public Service College&quot; was an incredibly valuable endeavor which made me develop my skills and professional insights<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"2ff393f6c7114a96cb333fdec73449b4.png\",\"user_id\":6,\"slug\":\"jerome-mwakyembe\"}','2023-12-15 08:58:59','2023-12-15 08:58:59'),(1289,6,'Announcement','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/announcements','{\"name_sw\":\"MAHAFALI YA 38 YA CHUO CHA UTUMISHI WA UMMA TANZANIA (TPSC)\",\"name_en\":\"MAHAFALI YA 38 YA CHUO CHA UTUMISHI WA UMMA TANZANIA (TPSC)\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>Kaimu Mkuu wa Chuo na Mtendaji Mkuu wa Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania anapenda kuwatangazia wahitimu wote na wadau wa Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma kwa ujumla kuwa Mahafali ya Thelathini na Nane (38) kwa Kampasi zote za Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma yatafanyika siku ya Ijumaa , tarehe 24 Novemba 2023 katika viwanja vya Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Kampasi ya Tabora, kuanzia saa tatu (03.00) asubuhi.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mgeni Rasmi anatarajiwa kuwa Waziri wa Nchi, Ofisi ya Rais, Menejimenti ya Utumishi wa Umma na Utawala Bora, Mh. Mhe. George B. Simbachawene (MB).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Majina ya wahitimu yanapatakana kwenye tuvuti ya Chuo&nbsp;<strong>(<\\/strong><em><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.tpsc.go.tz\\/\\\">www.tpsc.go.tz<\\/a><\\/em><strong>).<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Aidha, wahitimu wote wanahimizwa kuhudhuria mahafali hayo. Mazoezi (Rehearsal) yatafanyika siku ya Alhamisi tarehe 23 Novemba 2023 katika Kampasi ya Tabora saa nane (08.00) mchana.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Wahitimu wanatakiwa kuvaa suti zinazokubalika Chuoni (nyeusi au dark blue). Gharama ya Joho ni shilingi 30,000 kwa wahitimu wa Shahada ya kwanza na Skafu shilingi 10,000 kwa wahitimu wa Cheti na Stashahada.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Aidha, wahitimu mnatakiwa kuthibitisha ushiriki wenu kupitia namba. 0717152111 \\/0764775034\\/0784680077\\/071757452\\/0717574525<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>IMETOLEWA NA:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>KITENGO CHA MAWASILIANO NA MASOKO<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p>Kaimu Mkuu wa Chuo na Mtendaji Mkuu wa Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania anapenda kuwatangazia wahitimu wote na wadau wa Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma kwa ujumla kuwa Mahafali ya Thelathini na Nane (38) kwa Kampasi zote za Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma yatafanyika siku ya Ijumaa , tarehe 24 Novemba 2023 katika viwanja vya Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Kampasi ya Tabora, kuanzia saa tatu (03.00) asubuhi.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mgeni Rasmi anatarajiwa kuwa Waziri wa Nchi, Ofisi ya Rais, Menejimenti ya Utumishi wa Umma na Utawala Bora, Mh. Mhe. George B. Simbachawene (MB).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Majina ya wahitimu yanapatakana kwenye tuvuti ya Chuo&nbsp;<strong>(<\\/strong><em><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.tpsc.go.tz\\/\\\">www.tpsc.go.tz<\\/a><\\/em><strong>).<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Aidha, wahitimu wote wanahimizwa kuhudhuria mahafali hayo. Mazoezi (Rehearsal) yatafanyika siku ya Alhamisi tarehe 23 Novemba 2023 katika Kampasi ya Tabora saa nane (08.00) mchana.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Wahitimu wanatakiwa kuvaa suti zinazokubalika Chuoni (nyeusi au dark blue). Gharama ya Joho ni shilingi 30,000 kwa wahitimu wa Shahada ya kwanza na Skafu shilingi 10,000 kwa wahitimu wa Cheti na Stashahada.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Aidha, wahitimu mnatakiwa kuthibitisha ushiriki wenu kupitia namba. 0717152111 \\/0764775034\\/0784680077\\/071757452\\/0717574525<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>IMETOLEWA NA:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>KITENGO CHA MAWASILIANO NA MASOKO<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"slug\":\"mahafali-ya-38-ya-chuo-cha-utumishi-wa-umma-tanzania-tpsc\"}','2023-12-15 09:05:23','2023-12-15 09:05:23'),(1290,6,'PressRelease','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/press_releases/5','{\"id\":5,\"name_sw\":\"ACADEMIC AND ADMINISTRATION APPOINTMENTS\",\"name_en\":\"ACADEMIC AND ADMINISTRATION APPOINTMENTS\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>ACADEMIC AND ADMINISTRATION APPOINTMENTS<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p>ACADEMIC AND ADMINISTRATION APPOINTMENTS<\\/p>\",\"file_en\":\"\\/uploads\\/press_releases\\/en1702642142-ACADEMIC AND ADMINISTRATION APPOINTMENTS - PR.pdf\",\"file_sw\":\"\\/uploads\\/press_releases\\/sw1702642142-ACADEMIC AND ADMINISTRATION APPOINTMENTS - PR.pdf\",\"active\":\"1\",\"slug\":\"mapitio-ya-kikao-kazi-cha-utendaji-wa-tnbc-2\",\"user_id\":1,\"created_at\":\"2021-08-02T07:04:15.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2021-08-09T15:21:09.000000Z\"}','2023-12-15 09:09:02','2023-12-15 09:09:02'),(1291,6,'MenuItem','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/menu-items/99','{\"id\":99,\"title_sw\":\"Taarifa kwa Umma\",\"title_en\":\"Press Release\",\"status\":1,\"menu_id\":\"12\",\"url\":\"press-releases\",\"url_external\":null,\"link\":\"1\",\"parent\":89,\"position\":3,\"has_sidebar\":0,\"created_at\":\"2023-12-13T10:09:55.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-15T10:27:45.000000Z\"}','2023-12-15 09:10:28','2023-12-15 09:10:28'),(1292,6,'Announcement','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/announcements','{\"name_sw\":\"Mitihani ya watumishi wa Umma\",\"name_en\":\"Public Service Examinations\",\"content_sw\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\">Tanzania Public Service College (TPSC) is informing all the Public Service Examination Candidates that, the standard review courses for PSE will start on 19<sup>th<\\/sup> February, 2024 to 8<sup>th<\\/sup> March, 2024 at TPSC Dar es Salaam, Tabora, Mtwara Singida, Tanga and Mbeya Campuses. However, the Examinations (PSE) will be held from 11<sup>th<\\/sup> to 15<sup>th<\\/sup> &nbsp;&nbsp;March, 2024.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:white\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\\\">Tanzania Public Service College (TPSC) is informing all the Public Service Examination Candidates that, the standard revi