":\"07:00 AM-10:00PM\",\"location\":\"Dodoma\",\"title_en\":\"Board Meeting\",\"title_sw\":\"Kikao cha Bodi\",\"content_en\":\"<p>Board Meeting<\\/p>\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>Kikao cha Bodi<\\/p>\",\"active\":\"1\",\"photo_url\":\"f8254a84d68d2473b421a11a5ce1f0d7.png\",\"user_id\":6,\"slug\":\"board-meeting\"}','2023-12-15 13:02:31','2023-12-15 13:02:31'),(1397,6,'MenuItem','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/menu-items/94','{\"id\":94,\"title_sw\":\"Matukio\",\"title_en\":\"Events\",\"status\":1,\"menu_id\":\"12\",\"url\":\"events\",\"url_external\":null,\"link\":\"1\",\"parent\":89,\"position\":1,\"has_sidebar\":0,\"created_at\":\"2023-12-13T10:08:31.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-15T12:45:15.000000Z\"}','2023-12-15 13:03:39','2023-12-15 13:03:39'),(1398,6,'DocumentCategory','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/document-categories','{\"title_sw\":\"Makala\",\"title_en\":\"Featured Articles\",\"slug\":\"featured-articles\"}','2023-12-15 13:13:22','2023-12-15 13:13:22'),(1399,6,'Documents','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/documents','{\"title_sw\":\"TPSC KATIKA KUHUDUMIA WANANCHI\",\"title_en\":\"TPSC KATIKA KUHUDUMIA WANANCHI\",\"category_id\":\"16\",\"active\":\"1\",\"published_date\":\"2023-12-15\",\"file_sw\":\"sw-1702656907-MAKALA.pdf\",\"file_en\":\"en-1702656907-MAKALA.pdf\"}','2023-12-15 13:15:07','2023-12-15 13:15:07'),(1400,6,'MenuItem','store','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/menu-items','{\"menu_id\":\"12\",\"title_sw\":\"Makala\",\"title_en\":\"Featured Articles\",\"link\":\"1\",\"url_external\":null,\"url\":\"publications\\/featured-articles\",\"position\":9}','2023-12-15 13:17:01','2023-12-15 13:17:01'),(1401,6,'Administration','update','197.186.2.91','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/administration/15','{\"id\":15,\"salutation_en\":\"Mr.\",\"salutation_sw\":\"Ndg.\",\"fullname\":\"Elibarick Mushi\",\"position\":\"0\",\"title_sw\":\"Kaimu Mkurugenzi - Academic Supports Services\",\"title_en\":\"Ag. Director - Academic Supports Services\",\"content_sw\":\"<p>Bw. Elibarick Mushi aliteuliwa kushika nafasi ya Mkurugenzi wa Idara saidizi za Taaaluma tangu mwezi Novemba 2023. Kabla ya nafasi hiyo, amepata fursa ya kutumikia katika nafasi mbalimbali katika Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kama vile Kusimamia Kitengo cha Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki Ubora (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Kusimamia Kitengo cha TEHAMA (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Meneja Mafunzo (Miaka Minne), Mkuu wa Kitengo cha Usajili na Mitihani katika Kampasi (Miaka mitatu), na Mratibu wa TeHAMA katika Kampasi (Mwaka Mmoja). Kabla ya kujiunga na Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania, ametumika kama Mhadhiri Msaidizi, na Mhadhiri Mwandamizi katika chuo cha Kimataifa cha Kampala kwa kipindi cha miaka minne.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Akiwa na Uzoefu wa Miaka 13 kwenye tasnia ya mafunzo katika vyuo, ikiambatana na dhamira ya dhati ya kutumia TEHAMA kuboresha utendaji kazi ya taasisi, Elibarick amekuwa na mchango mkubwa katika kuibua vipaji vya kizazi kipya cha wataalamu wa TEHAMA pamoja na kuwahamasisha waanchuo wa fani nyingine kutumia vema TEHAMA katika kuongeza tija kwenye majuku yao kazini. Utaalamu wake umejikita katika maeneo ya Lugha za Computer, Mifumo Mtandao, Utengenezaji Mifumo, Uundaji wa Kanzidata, na Programu rahisishi za kazi za Ofisi.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mbali na kushiri katika kazi za taaaluma,&nbsp; fursa aliyopata ya kutumika katika nafasi mbalimbali za uongozi na utawala zimempa uzoefu katika maeneo ya Utawala, Uundaji na Usimamzi wa Utekelezaji wa Mitaala ya vyuo, Uundaji wa Sera, Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki ubora wa Vyuo na Uratibu wa Kazi za kamati za taaluma vyuoni.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Kielimu, Elibarick ana Shahada ya Kwanza ya Menenimenti ya Mifumo na Shahada ya Uzamili ya Mifumo.<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p>Mr. Elibarick Mushi assumed the role of Director of Academic Support Services in November 2023. Prior to his current position, he served in various key roles at Tanzania Public Service College, including Head of Quality Assurance (1.5 years), Head of ICT (1.5 years), Manager of Programmes (4 years), Campus Head of Admission and Examination Unit (3 years), and Campus ICT Coordinator (1 year). Before joining TPSC, he server for four years as an Assistant Lecturer and Tutorial Assistant at Kampala International University.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With 13 years of dedicated experience in higher education, coupled with passion about utilizing technology to enhance business operations, Elibarick has played a pivotal role in shaping the next generation of ICT professionals and inspiring students from diverse fields to leverage ICT for improved performance in their respective professions. His training expertise spans computer programming, web applications development, Information Systems, database design, and office applications.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In addition to his teaching roles, Elibarick&#39;s exposure to managerial and administrative duties has honed his skills in Administration, Curriculum Development and Implementation, Policy Formulation, Quality Assurance in Colleges, and Academic Committees&rsquo; Management.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Elibarick holds a Bachelor&#39;s degree in Management Information Systems and a Master&#39;s degree in Information Systems.<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"882fc34c01729e46b8ff8307fd754e2e.png\",\"email\":\"elibarick.mushi@tpsc.go.tz\",\"phone\":\"0753860432\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-14T11:49:50.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-14T12:23:16.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"director\"}','2023-12-16 12:02:00','2023-12-16 12:02:00'),(1402,6,'Administration','update','197.186.2.91','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/administration/15','{\"id\":15,\"salutation_en\":\"Mr.\",\"salutation_sw\":\"Ndg.\",\"fullname\":\"Elibarick Mushi\",\"position\":\"0\",\"title_sw\":\"Kaimu Mkurugenzi - Academic Supports Services\",\"title_en\":\"Ag. Director - Academic Supports Services\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Bw. Elibarick Mushi aliteuliwa kushika nafasi ya Mkurugenzi wa Idara saidizi za Taaaluma (Kaimu) tangu mwezi Novemba 2023. Kabla ya nafasi hiyo, amepata fursa ya kutumikia katika nafasi mbalimbali katika Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kama vile Kusimamia Kitengo cha Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki Ubora (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Kusimamia Kitengo cha TEHAMA (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Meneja Mafunzo (Miaka Minne), Mkuu wa Kitengo cha Usajili na Mitihani katika Kampasi (Miaka mitatu), na Mratibu wa TeHAMA katika Kampasi (Mwaka Mmoja). Kabla ya kujiunga na Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania, ametumika kama Mhadhiri Msaidizi, na Mhadhiri Mwandamizi katika chuo cha Kimataifa cha Kampala kwa kipindi cha miaka minne.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Akiwa na Uzoefu wa Miaka 13 kwenye tasnia ya mafunzo katika vyuo, ikiambatana na dhamira ya dhati ya kutumia TEHAMA kuboresha utendaji kazi ya taasisi, Elibarick amekuwa na mchango mkubwa katika kuibua vipaji vya kizazi kipya cha wataalamu wa TEHAMA pamoja na kuwahamasisha waanchuo wa fani nyingine kutumia vema TEHAMA katika kuongeza tija kwenye majuku yao kazini. Utaalamu wake umejikita katika maeneo ya Lugha za Computer, Mifumo Mtandao, Utengenezaji Mifumo, Uundaji wa Kanzidata, na Programu rahisishi za kazi za Ofisi.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Mbali na kushiri katika kazi za taaaluma,&nbsp; fursa aliyopata ya kutumika katika nafasi mbalimbali za uongozi na utawala zimempa uzoefu katika maeneo ya Utawala, Uundaji na Usimamzi wa Utekelezaji wa Mitaala ya vyuo, Uundaji wa Sera, Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki ubora wa Vyuo na Uratibu wa Kazi za kamati za taaluma vyuoni.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Kielimu, Elibarick ana Shahada ya Kwanza ya Menenimenti ya Mifumo na Shahada ya Uzamili ya Mifumo.<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Mr. Elibarick Mushi assumed the role of Director of Academic Support Services (Acting) in November 2023. Prior to his current position, he served in various key roles at Tanzania Public Service College, including Head of Quality Assurance (1.5 years), Head of ICT (1.5 years), Manager of Programmes (4 years), Campus Head of Admission and Examination Unit (3 years), and Campus ICT Coordinator (1 year). Before joining TPSC, he server for four years as an Assistant Lecturer and Tutorial Assistant at Kampala International University.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">With 13 years of dedicated experience in higher education, coupled with passion about utilizing technology to enhance business operations, Elibarick has played a pivotal role in shaping the next generation of ICT professionals and inspiring students from diverse fields to leverage ICT for improved performance in their respective professions. His training expertise spans computer programming, web applications development, Information Systems, database design, and office applications.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">In addition to his teaching roles, Elibarick&#39;s exposure to managerial and administrative duties has honed his skills in Administration, Curriculum Development and Implementation, Policy Formulation, Quality Assurance in Colleges, and Academic Committees&rsquo; Management.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Elibarick holds a Bachelor&#39;s degree in Management Information Systems and a Master&#39;s degree in Information Systems.<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"882fc34c01729e46b8ff8307fd754e2e.png\",\"email\":\"elibarick.mushi@tpsc.go.tz\",\"phone\":\"0753860432\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-14T11:49:50.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-16T15:02:00.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"director\"}','2023-12-16 12:03:55','2023-12-16 12:03:55'),(1403,6,'Administration','update','197.186.2.91','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/administration/15','{\"id\":15,\"salutation_en\":\"Mr.\",\"salutation_sw\":\"Ndg.\",\"fullname\":\"Elibarick Mushi\",\"position\":\"0\",\"title_sw\":\"Kaimu Mkurugenzi - Academic Supports Services\",\"title_en\":\"Ag. Director - Academic Supports Services\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Bw. Elibarick Mushi aliteuliwa kushika nafasi ya Mkurugenzi wa Idara saidizi za Taaaluma (Kaimu) tangu mwezi Novemba 2023. Kabla ya nafasi hiyo, amepata fursa ya kutumikia katika nafasi mbalimbali katika Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kama vile Kusimamia Kitengo cha Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki Ubora (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Kusimamia Kitengo cha TEHAMA (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Meneja Mafunzo (Miaka Minne), Mkuu wa Kitengo cha Usajili na Mitihani katika Kampasi (Miaka mitatu), na Mratibu wa TeHAMA katika Kampasi (Mwaka Mmoja). Kabla ya kujiunga na Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania, ametumika kama Mhadhiri Msaidizi, na Mhadhiri Mwandamizi katika chuo cha Kimataifa cha Kampala kwa kipindi cha miaka minne.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Akiwa na Uzoefu wa Miaka 13 kwenye tasnia ya mafunzo katika vyuo, ikiambatana na dhamira ya dhati ya kutumia TEHAMA kuboresha utendaji kazi ya taasisi, Elibarick amekuwa na mchango mkubwa katika kuibua vipaji vya kizazi kipya cha wataalamu wa TEHAMA pamoja na kuwahamasisha waanchuo wa fani nyingine kutumia vema TEHAMA katika kuongeza tija kwenye majuku yao kazini. Utaalamu wake umejikita katika maeneo ya Lugha za Computer, Mifumo Mtandao, Utengenezaji Mifumo, Uundaji wa Kanzidata, na Programu rahisishi za kazi za Ofisi.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mbali na kushiri katika kazi za taaaluma,&nbsp; fursa aliyopata ya kutumika katika nafasi mbalimbali za uongozi na utawala zimempa uzoefu katika maeneo ya Utawala, Uundaji na Usimamzi wa Utekelezaji wa Mitaala ya vyuo, Uundaji wa Sera, Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki ubora wa Vyuo na Uratibu wa Kazi za kamati za taaluma vyuoni.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Kielimu, Elibarick ana Shahada ya Kwanza ya Menenimenti ya Mifumo na Shahada ya Uzamili ya Mifumo.<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mr. Elibarick Mushi assumed the role of Director of Academic Support Services (Acting) in November 2023. Prior to his current position, he served in various key roles at Tanzania Public Service College, including Head of Quality Assurance (1.5 years), Head of ICT (1.5 years), Manager of Programmes (4 years), Campus Head of Admission and Examination Unit (3 years), and Campus ICT Coordinator (1 year). Before joining TPSC, he served for four years as an Assistant Lecturer and Tutorial Assistant at Kampala International University.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">With 13 years of dedicated experience in higher education, coupled with passion about utilizing technology to enhance business operations, Elibarick has played a pivotal role in shaping the next generation of ICT professionals and inspiring students from diverse fields to leverage ICT for improved performance in their respective professions. His training expertise spans computer programming, web applications development, Information Systems, database design, and office applications.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">In addition to his teaching roles, Elibarick&#39;s exposure to managerial and administrative duties has honed his skills in Administration, Curriculum Development and Implementation, Policy Formulation, Quality Assurance in Colleges, and Academic Committees&rsquo; Management.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Elibarick holds a Bachelor&#39;s degree in Management Information Systems and a Master&#39;s degree in Information Systems.<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"882fc34c01729e46b8ff8307fd754e2e.png\",\"email\":\"elibarick.mushi@tpsc.go.tz\",\"phone\":\"0753860432\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-14T11:49:50.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-16T15:03:55.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"director\"}','2023-12-16 12:05:54','2023-12-16 12:05:54'),(1404,6,'Administration','update','197.186.2.91','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/administration/15','{\"i