d ornare est dignissim non. Nunc suscipit efficitur lorem sed rutrum. Nam odio orci, finibus in ullamcorper in, gravida ut ante. Donec sed justo porta, semper nibh non, rhoncus neque. Etiam vel est ut nunc fermentum ullamcorper. Sed dapibus tempus aliquam.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Quisque vulputate lobortis consequat. Sed tincidunt a dui et dapibus. Duis at metus et ex viverra ullamcorper. Aenean eget eros lorem. Curabitur elementum tellus eget condimentum feugiat. Proin blandit lobortis neque at mattis. Fusce mollis sem elit, eu ullamcorper ex auctor a. Sed posuere tristique libero sit amet ornare. Quisque eu ullamcorper turpis. Praesent tristique pharetra quam, id dapibus turpis viverra sed.<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"4cb1079629c181bd699f9ba18e9a057a.jpeg\",\"email\":\"sijali.korojelo@tpsc.go.tz\",\"phone\":\"0766000000\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-14T11:52:23.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-19T11:03:12.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"director-2\"}','2023-12-19 08:03:16','2023-12-19 08:03:16'),(1465,6,'Administration','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/administration/15','{\"id\":15,\"salutation_en\":\"Mr.\",\"salutation_sw\":\"Ndg.\",\"fullname\":\"Elibarick Mushi\",\"position\":\"0\",\"title_sw\":\"Kaimu Mkurugenzi - Huduma Wezeshi za Taaluma\",\"title_en\":\"Ag. Director - Academic Supports Services\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Bw. Elibarick Mushi aliteuliwa kushika nafasi ya Mkurugenzi wa huduma wezeshi za Taaluma (Kaimu) tangu mwezi Novemba 2023. Kabla ya nafasi hiyo, amepata fursa ya kutumikia katika nafasi mbalimbali katika Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania kama vile Kusimamia Kitengo cha Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki Ubora (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Kusimamia Kitengo cha TEHAMA (Mwaka mmoja na nusu), Meneja Mafunzo (Miaka Minne), Mkuu wa Kitengo cha Usajili na Mitihani katika Kampasi (Miaka mitatu), na Mratibu wa TeHAMA katika Kampasi (Mwaka Mmoja). Kabla ya kujiunga na Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania, ametumika kama Mhadhiri Msaidizi, na Mhadhiri Mwandamizi katika chuo cha Kimataifa cha Kampala kwa kipindi cha miaka minne.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Akiwa na Uzoefu wa Miaka 13 kwenye tasnia ya mafunzo katika vyuo, ikiambatana na dhamira ya dhati ya kutumia TEHAMA kuboresha utendaji kazi za taasisi, Elibarick amekuwa na mchango mkubwa katika kuibua vipaji vya kizazi kipya cha wataalamu wa TEHAMA pamoja na kuwahamasisha wanachuo wa fani nyingine kutumia vema TEHAMA katika kuongeza tija kwenye majukumu yao kazini. Maeneo yake ya Ubobevu kitaaluma ni Lugha za Computer, Mifumo Mtandao, Utengenezaji Mifumo, Uundaji wa Kanzidata, na Programu rahisishi za kazi za Ofisi.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mbali na kushiri katika kazi za taaluma,&nbsp; fursa aliyopata ya kutumika katika nafasi mbalimbali za uongozi na utawala zimempa uzoefu katika maeneo ya Utawala, Uundaji na Usimamizi wa Utekelezaji wa Mitaala ya vyuo, Uundaji wa Sera, Udhibiti\\/Uhakiki ubora wa Vyuo na Uratibu wa Kazi za kamati za taaluma vyuoni.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Kielimu, Elibarick ana Shahada ya Kwanza ya Menejimenti ya Mifumo na Shahada ya Uzamili ya Mifumo.<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Mr. Elibarick Mushi assumed the role of Director of Academic Support Services (Acting) in November 2023. Prior to his current position, he served in various key roles at Tanzania Public Service College, including Head of Quality Assurance (1.5 years), Head of ICT (1.5 years), Manager of Programmes (4 years), Campus Head of Admission and Examination Unit (3 years), and Campus ICT Coordinator (1 year). Before joining TPSC, he served for four years as an Assistant Lecturer and Tutorial Assistant at Kampala International University.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">With 13 years of dedicated experience in higher education, coupled with passion about utilizing technology to enhance business operations, Elibarick has played a pivotal role in shaping the next generation of ICT professionals and inspiring students from diverse fields to leverage ICT for improved performance in their respective professions. His training expertise spans computer programming, web applications development, Information Systems, database design, and office applications.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">In addition to his teaching roles, Elibarick&#39;s exposure to managerial and administrative duties has honed his skills in Administration, Curriculum Development and Implementation, Policy Formulation, Quality Assurance in Colleges, and Academic Committees&rsquo; Management.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Elibarick holds a Bachelor&#39;s degree in Management Information Systems and a Master&#39;s degree in Information Systems.<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"b1231bf5b1de054f090b00c11b204416.jpeg\",\"email\":\"elibarick.mushi@tpsc.go.tz\",\"phone\":\"0753860432\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-14T11:49:50.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-18T12:57:06.000000Z\",\"slug\":\"director\"}','2023-12-19 08:07:01','2023-12-19 08:07:01'),(1466,6,'Administration','update','41.59.251.78','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/administration/22','{\"id\":22,\"salutation_en\":\"Ms.\",\"salutation_sw\":\"Bi.\",\"fullname\":\"Zawadi Rashid\",\"position\":\"0\",\"title_sw\":\"Mkurugenzi\",\"title_en\":\"Director\",\"content_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Lorem 