ook is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, &quot;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..&quot;, comes from a line in section 1.10.32.<\\/p>\",\"description_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of &quot;de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum&quot; (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, &quot;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..&quot;, comes from a line in section 1.10.32.<\\/p>\",\"target_audience_sw\":\"<p>Watumishi wote<\\/p>\",\"target_audience_en\":\"<p>All Staff<\\/p>\",\"course_overview_sw\":\"<p>abcd<\\/p>\",\"course_overview_en\":\"<p>abcd<\\/p>\",\"expected_benefit_sw\":\"<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of &quot;de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum&quot; (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, &quot;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..&quot;, comes from a line in section 1.10.32.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"expected_benefit_en\":\"<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of &quot;de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum&quot; (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, &quot;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..&quot;, comes from a line in section 1.10.32.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"course_coodinator_sw\":\"<p>addafa<\\/p>\",\"course_coodinator_en\":\"<p>addafa<\\/p>\",\"course_detail_id\":17,\"course_type\":2}','2024-01-15 15:17:58','2024-01-15 15:17:58'),(1535,6,'Campus','update','41.222.181.218','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/campuses/10','{\"id\":10,\"particulars_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Tanzania Public Service College &ndash; Singida Campus is one of the six (6) Campuses of the Tanzania Public Service College (TPSC). The Campus was established in July 2011, being the fourth campus to be established among the six campuses of TPSC. Its establishment was a result of instructions issued by Prime Minister Hon. Mizengo Pinda on 23rd November 2009 during inauguration of Tanzania Public Service College Mtwara Campus. Singida Campus is located along airport road in Mandewa Ward at Singida Municipality &ndash;Singida Region.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Kampasi ya Singida ipo Barabara ya Uwanja wa Ndege, Kata ya Mandewa -Manispaa ya Singida. Kampasi ya Singida inatoa kozi mbalimbali kuanzia ngazi ya astashahada na stashahada. Miongoni mwa kozi hizo ni pamoja na astashahada ya utunzaji wa kumbukumbu, astashahada ya uhazili, astashahada ya menejimenti ya rasilimaliwatu na astashahada ya utawala wa umma (NTA,4) pamoja na&nbsp; stashahada ya utunzaji wa kumbukumbu, stashahada ya uhazili, stashahada ya menejimenti ya rasilimaliwatu na stashahada ya utawala wa umma (NTA 5&amp; 6). Aidha, Kampasi ya Singida ni kituo cha mafunzo ya muda mfupi kwa watumishi wa umma, shauri za kitaalamu na ni kituo&nbsp; cha&nbsp; mafunzo na mitihani kwa watumishi wa umma<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"student_services_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Ili kuwasaidia wanachuo kupata ujuzi kwa lengo la kukuza weledi wao na maendeleo ya taaluma&nbsp; zao&nbsp; katika fani mbalimbali walizochagua , kampasi ya Singida ipo katika mazingira mazuri ambayo yana-:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma za&nbsp; uhakika za&nbsp; kifedha na chakula zinazotolewa na taasisi mbalimbali za kifedha na chakula ili &nbsp;kusaidia upatikanaji rahisi wa huduma za fedha na chakula kwa gharama nafuu<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Hali ya hewa nzuri&nbsp; inayofungamanishwa&nbsp; na mazingira mazuri ya kujisomea&nbsp; na kujifunza <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma nzuri za hosteli na malazi zinazopatikana kwa bei rahisi. Kampasi inatoa huduma za hosteli zinazopatikana ndani na nje ya chuo. Hosteli za nje ya kampasi zinapatikana kwa kushirikiana na wamiliki binafsi lakini chini ya usimamizi wa menejimenti ya Kampasi.&nbsp; Ghrama za hostei kwa muhula ni kati ya Tsh. 150,000-200,000 kutegemeana na ubora &nbsp;wa hosteli husika <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma nzuri za&nbsp; afya ambazo hutolewa kupitia vituo vya kutolea huduma za afya vinavyomilikiwa na serikali na taasisi binafsi&nbsp; hususan Hospitali ya Manispaa ya Singida, Hospitali ya Rufaa ya Mkoa , Kituo cha afya cha Tumaini, Kituo cha Afya MICO n,k. Vituo vyote hivi vya kutolea huduma za afya vinafikika kirahisi, vinatoa huduma bora&nbsp; na vipo karibu na chuo. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma za kuabudu kwa dini zote na madhehebu yote. Kampasi ya Singida ipo karibu kabisa na nyumba mbalimbali za kuabudia (makanisa na misikiti) kwa wanachuo wa dini zote. Aidha, Kampasi ya Singida imeruhusu wanachuo kutumia ukumbi wa chuo kwa ajili ya kuabudia pale unapohitajika<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma za viwanja vya michezo mbalimbali ili kuwapa wanachuo pamoja na walimu wao &nbsp;fursa ya kushiriki kwenye michezo mbalimbali ili kuimarisha afya zao &nbsp;na kuboresha maendeleo ya taaluma zao. Baadhi ya viwanja vya&nbsp; michezo vilivyopo ni pamoja na viwanja vya mpira wa miguu, mpira wa pete&nbsp; na mpira wa wavu <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma za bima za&nbsp; afya ambazo zinatolewa kwa ushirikiano na Mfuko wa Taifa wa Bima ya Afya (NHIF) ili kurahisisha upatikanaji wa afya bora na kwa wakati kwa wanachuo. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma za ushauri&nbsp; hususan ushauri kuhusu mambo ya kiafya,&nbsp; kitaaluma, kiuchumi na kifedha, na kisaikolojia&nbsp; hutolewa kwa wanachuo wenye uhitaji na wanachuo wote kwa ujumla <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Huduma nzuri za ulinzi na usalama wakati wote hivyo kuwasaidia wanachuo kujifunza pasipo hofu zozote za kiusalama.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"facilities_sw\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Kampasi ya Singida inatoa huduma zake za kitaaluma kupitia kwenye madarasa ya kisasa na yanayopitisha hewa ya kutosha, maabara za kisasa za kuchapia, maabara za kisasa za komputa, maktaba nzuri yenye vitabu vya kisasa, mtandao wa kutosha kuwezesha wanachuo kujitafutia mahitaji yao ya kujifunzia kwenye vyanzo mbalimbali, n.k. Aidha, Kampasi ina watumishi ( Walimu na Wasiowalimu) wanaojituma, wenye weledi, hamasa na wenye vipaji vya kutosha kufanya kazi ya kuwajengea uwezo wanachuo katika Nyanja tofauti tofauti kwa utiifu na uaminifu mkubwa. &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"contacts_sw\":\"<p><em>Mkurugenzi wa Kampasi<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>S.L.P 1534<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Singida<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Simu:<\\/em><\\/strong><em>&nbsp;<\\/em><em>+255 26 2502933\\/3082<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Nukushi<\\/em><\\/strong><em>&nbsp;<\\/em><em>+255 26 250 3082<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Barua Pepe:<\\/em><\\/strong><em>&nbsp;<\\/em><em>singida@tpsc.go.tz<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"particulars_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Kampasi ya Singida ni miongoni mwa Kampasi sita za Chuo cha Utumishi wa Umma Tanzania.&nbsp; Kampasi ya Singida&nbsp;&nbsp; ilianzishwa rasmi Mwezi wa Saba (7) mwaka 2011 ikiwa ni kampasi ya nne kuanzishwa kati ya Kampasi sita za Chuo.&nbsp; Kuanzishwa kwa Kampasi ya Singida ni utekelezaji wa maelekezo aliyoyatoa aliyekuwa Waziri Mkuu <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11.0pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:&quot;Footlight MT Light&quot;,serif\\\">Mh. Mizengo Pinda tarehe 23 Novemba, 2009 wakati akifungua kampasi ya Mtwara. Kamapasi ya Singida ipo Barabara ya Uwanja wa Ndege, Kata ya Mandewa -Manispaa ya Singida<\\/span><\\/span>.<\\/p>\",\"course_offered_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">The Campus offers a wide range of programmes from Certificate to Diploma levels. The courses offered include Basic Technician Certificate in Secretarial Studies (BTCSS) &ndash; NTA 4; Basic Technician Certificate in Records Management (BTCRM) - NTA 4; Basic Technician Certificate in Human Resource Management (BTCHRM) &ndash; NTA 4; Basic Technician Certificate in Public Administration (BTCPA) &ndash; NTA 4; Ordinary Diploma in Secretarial Studies (ODSS) &ndash; NTA 5 &amp; 6; Ordinary Diploma in Records Management (ODRM) (NTA 5 &amp; 6); Ordinary Diploma in Public Administration (ODPA) &ndash; NTA 5 &amp; 6 and Ordinary Diploma in Human Resource Management (ODHRM)&ndash;NTA 5 &amp; 6. Likewise, the Campus offers short courses and consultant services to different stakeholders in the public and private sector. It is also the centre for coordinating and conducting Public Service Examinations (PSE) to public servants. Singida Campus follows Competence Based Education Training (CBET) curricula and positions itself to practice all its endeavors at the highest level of standards<\\/p>\",\"student_services_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">To enable students acquire necessary skills for professionalism and career development in different areas of specialization the campus has ensured-:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">a)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Reliable catering and banking services to facilitate &nbsp;availability of food and banking services at affordable cost<br \\/>\\r\\nb)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Good climatic condition surrounded by greenish environment that makes learning and studying environment conducive.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\nc)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;The accommodation services: The campus offers a range of quality accommodation services both on-campus and off-campus. Off campus accommodation services are handled in collaboration with private owners of hostels but under the management and control of Campus management. The services are charged at the rate of TZS. 150,000-200,000\\/= per &nbsp;semester&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\nd)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Government and private owned health facilities including Singida Regional Referral Hospital, Singida Municipal Hospital, Tumaini Health Centre and MICO Health Centre that provide high quality, responsive and sustainable health services are all located nearby the Campus.<br \\/>\\r\\ne)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Religious facilities including churches for Christian students and Mosque for Muslims students are available for enhancing students&rsquo; spiritual life. Apart from that, campus provides building for worshipping services for all Christians and Muslims students who need extra religious services.<br \\/>\\r\\nf)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Sports and games facilities that aim to promote overall health and mental ability of the students and teachers. Sports facilities available include football pitches, netball, and volleyball among others.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\ng)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Health Insurance services which are provided in collaboration with National Health Insurance Funds (NHIF) are ensured to students for ease and quality acquisition of health services at the affordable cost.<br \\/>\\r\\nh)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Counseling services that aims to offer services targeting health related concerns; academic (teaching and learning) concerns; psycho-social concerns; economic and financial concerns and other personal concerns. Likewise, the section commensurate with provision of high-quality services that nurture students to engage in academic and social development effectively.<\\/p>\",\"facilities_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">The campus provides academic services in well ventilated and modern classrooms, laboratories (both typing and computer laboratories) with a well-equipped library that contain modern and current books, internet and learning facilities. Teaching and learning activities are facilitated by well and highly qualified, motivated, committed and talented facilitators who are eager to serve the customers with high level of loyalty and integrity.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contacts_en\":\"<p><em>Campus Director,<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Tanzania Public Service College<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>P.O. Box 1534<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Singida<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Phone: +255 26 2502933\\/3082<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Fax: +255 26 250 3082<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Email: singida@tpsc.go.tz<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"slug\":\"singida-campus\",\"title_sw\":\"Kampasi  ya Singida\",\"title_en\":\"Singida Campus\",\"created_at\":\"2024-01-11T10:15:46.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2024-01-11T07:15:46.000000Z\"}','2024-01-17 11:36:46','2024-01-17 11:36:46'),(1536,1,'Documents','update','154.118.227.58','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/documents/11','{\"id\":11,\"title_sw\":\"Waziri Simbachawene awaonya Watumishi kuwadharau Wananchi\",\"title_en\":\"Waziri Simbachawene awaonya Watumishi kuwadharau Wananchi\",\"file_sw\":\"sw-1702987822-MAKALA.pdf\",\"file_en\":\"en-1702987822-MAKALA.pdf\",\"active\":\"0\",\"published_date\":\"2023-12-19\",\"category_id\":\"16\",\"created_at\":\"2023-12-19T12:10:22.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-12-19T12:10:22.000000Z\"}','2024-02-03 08:40:18','2024-02-03 08:40:18'),(1537,1,'Documents','update','154.118.227.58','http://demo81.eganet.go.tz/tpsc/cms/documents/11','{\"id\":11,\"title_sw\":\"Waziri Simbachawene awaonya Watumishi kuwadharau Wananchi\",\"title_en\":\"Waziri Simbachawene awaonya Watumishi kuwadharau Wananchi\",\"file_sw\":\"sw-1702987822-MAKALA.pdf\",\"file_en\":\"en-1702987822-MAKALA.pdf\",\"active\":\"1\",\"published_date\":\"2023-12-19\",\"ca